    • A Future Battle For Compute

      Artificial super intelligence is, by definition, artificial intelligence which far exceeds human intelligence. If artificial super intelligence one day becomes reality, we will find ourselves far too inferior to intellectually defend ourselves from it. Instead, we will have to employ the help of another artificial super intelligent agent.
